38:28.266 --> 38:29.633
I was your father's friend.

38:29.700 --> 38:31.433
Hey, who's your reliable source,
huh?

38:31.500 --> 38:33.300
Some nut job
from the whack shack?

38:33.367 --> 38:34.433
- Never mind.

38:34.500 --> 38:36.367
I'll tell you who he is,
