49:01.867 --> 49:04.633
to be--well,
to be a family again,

49:04.700 --> 49:07.900
to ease Harry
back into your life.

49:07.967 --> 49:09.300
- And?

49:09.367 --> 49:11.266
- Well, they're waiting
in the parking lot.

49:11.333 --> 49:13.900
Harry won't get out of the car.

49:16.633 --> 49:19.200
Oh, no.

49:23.066 --> 49:25.200
- Son, son.

49:25.266 --> 49:27.066
He's six years old.

49:27.133 --> 49:29.133
