49:32.967 --> 49:34.767
- It's okay, don't force him.

49:34.834 --> 49:37.800
- We'll try again tomorrow.

49:39.100 --> 49:40.200
- No.
No.

49:43.166 --> 49:45.033
Let's just hold off, okay?

49:45.100 --> 49:46.266
My parole hearing's on Thursday.

49:46.333 --> 49:48.166
If I get paroled,

49:48.233 --> 49:51.734
I can see him at home.
- Are you sure?

49:51.800 --> 49:53.934
- Yes, I can wait.

49:54.000 --> 49:55.033
I can wait.

49:55.100 --> 49:56.967
It's just a couple more days.

49:57.033 --> 49:58.066
- Right.

49:58.133 --> 50:00.333
This time I know
the parole board

50:00.400 --> 50:02.834
is going to let you out.
I know it !

50:02.900 --> 50:06.834
In the bottom of my heart,
I know that you will be free.

50:12.800 --> 50:15.166
So, uh...

50:15.233 --> 50:17.533
tell me,
how does he look, my son?

50:17.600 --> 50:20.867
- Oh, well...

50:21.900 --> 50:25.033
Like his father.

50:29.567 --> 50:32.533
He has his mother's eyes.

50:42.567 --> 50:46.433
So you're going to see Chris
to talk about the appeal, right?

50:46.500 --> 50:47.700
- Yes.

50:52.834 --> 50:54.734
- Will you give him my love?

51:02.300 --> 51:04.133
- Our current strategy
is to focus

51:04.200 --> 51:06.567
on the credibility
of the prosecution's eyewitness.

51:06.633 --> 51:09.367
Uh...
- Jerry Heekin.

51:09.433 --> 51:11.200
- We've just discovered that

51:11.266 --> 51:14.433
he'd been arrested twice
for dealing crack cocaine.

51:14.500 --> 51:16.266
- How come my other
motherfucking lawyer

51:16.333 --> 51:18.700
didn't know that?

51:18.767 --> 51:22.100
- Well, like the kids say,
he sucked.

51:28.500 --> 51:31.633
Gotta calm down there,
Mr. Beecher.

51:31.700 --> 51:34.000
Gum?
- No, thank you.

51:36.367 --> 51:37.767
- You don't like me, do you?

51:37.834 --> 51:39.734
That's beside the point.

51:39.800 --> 51:41.834
I don't have to like you
to defend you.

51:41.900 --> 51:45.233
And my son--
- Loves me.

51:45.300 --> 51:47.333
That bother you?

51:48.367 --> 51:50.166
- Yes.

51:50.233 --> 51:52.734
- That he loves a man
or that he loves me?

51:52.800 --> 51:54.066
- We're finished for the day.

51:54.133 --> 51:55.667
- Your Honor,
please instruct the witness

51:55.734 --> 51:57.333
to answer the question.

51:57.400 --> 51:59.166
- All right.

51:59.233 --> 52:01.834
I find you despicable.

52:01.900 --> 52:04.300
Happy?

52:10.133 --> 52:13.066
- Just another notch in my gun.

52:13.133 --> 52:15.000
- The trial
of Mayor Wilson Loewen

52:15.066 --> 52:17.233
continued today at
the Bankhead State Courthouse.

52:17.300 --> 52:19.133
Loewen was indicted
for his involvement

52:19.200 --> 52:20.867
in the 1963 murder

52:20.934 --> 52:24.033
of two 10-year-old
African-American girls.

52:24.100 --> 52:26.100
Prosecutors alleged that Loewen,

52:26.166 --> 52:28.734
who was the Jackson County
sheriff at the time,

52:28.800 --> 52:30.333
aided and abetted

52:30.400 --> 52:33.333
members of the Ku Klux Klan
in the brutal slaying.

52:39.367 --> 52:42.133
- I beg your pardon.

52:43.400 --> 52:45.467
Guard!

52:50.567 --> 52:52.200
Guard!
Guard!

52:52.266 --> 52:55.734
Guard!
Oh!

52:55.800 --> 52:57.133
No!
Ah!

53:03.767 --> 53:05.266
No.

53:14.433 --> 53:16.767
- These are live images
from the east side of the city.

53:16.834 --> 53:19.567
Looting and burning have
continued for several hours,

53:19.633 --> 53:21.400
sparked
by Governor James Devlin's

53:21.467 --> 53:22.800
off-the-record comment

53:22.867 --> 53:24.567
that he would pardon
Wilson Loewen

53:24.633 --> 53:25.967
if the mayor is convicted.

53:26.033 --> 53:27.700
- First, let me announce

53:27.767 --> 53:31.133
that we have put
the National Guard on alert,

53:31.200 --> 53:32.967
though I sincerely hope

53:33.033 --> 53:34.633
there'll be no need
to activate it.

53:34.700 --> 53:36.633
Let me stress that violence,
especially rioting...

53:36.700 --> 53:38.967
- We cannot lose control here.
I want the prison locked down.

53:39.033 --> 53:40.567
- It never solved anything.
- Now go on.

53:40.633 --> 53:42.033
- The only thing that's
got me more confused

53:42.100 --> 53:44.834
than the rioting itself
is the reason for it.

53:44.900 --> 53:47.133
I am an innocent man,

53:47.200 --> 53:50.834
and yet you are destroying
your stores, your cars,

53:50.900 --> 53:53.333
your neighborhoods,
all based on hearsay

53:53.400 --> 53:57.233
With regards to a verdict
that not only has yet passed,

53:57.300 --> 53:59.033
but that will ultimately...
- Stay calm

53:59.100 --> 54:01.734
and preferably indoors.
- My brothers and sisters,

54:01.800 --> 54:03.667
we must stop the violence
on our streets.

54:03.734 --> 54:05.567
- I have spent my life trying
to make it a better place...

54:05.633 --> 54:07.967
- By rioting, by looting,
by destroying...

54:08.033 --> 54:09.567
- And my heart breaks
to see my city being torn down.

54:09.633 --> 54:11.200
- We are doing more
to damage our community

54:11.266 --> 54:13.333
than Mayor Loewen has.
- I am an innocent man....

54:13.400 --> 54:15.400
- There's no victory to be won

54:15.467 --> 54:18.800
when we address hate with hate.

54:18.867 --> 54:20.834
Let us take back our city
with love...

54:20.900 --> 54:23.066
-  Oh see now preacher 

54:23.133 --> 54:25.567
 You ought to been there 

54:25.633 --> 54:29.700
 Sitting in God's kingdom 

54:29.767 --> 54:33.834
 To see old Jordan roll 

54:33.900 --> 54:36.000
 I seen her roll 

54:36.066 --> 54:39.533
 Oh Jordan roll 

54:39.600 --> 54:43.767
 Roll Jordan roll 

54:43.834 --> 54:46.867
 I wanna get to heaven 

54:46.934 --> 54:50.033
 When I die 

54:50.100 --> 54:51.166
 Yeah 

54:51.233 --> 54:52.367
 To see 

54:53.400 --> 54:59.033
 Old Jordan roll 

54:59.100 --> 55:01.667
 Yeah, yeah 

55:02.934 --> 55:04.166
Rest in peace.
